      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear and tear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, but it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to address minor leaks and aged belts. It is a solid, functional choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
